 It's my karate.

1:10:35.940 --> 1:10:37.940
 It's not my wrestling.

1:10:37.940 --> 1:10:43.940
 I'm very good at timing my opponent and getting in

1:10:43.940 --> 1:10:45.940
 with my explosivity.

