 So I instigate the takedown by a fake, then I take him down.

1:11:07.180 --> 1:11:10.980
 And reactive is when he's, I'm baiting him to throw something

1:11:10.980 --> 1:11:11.980
 then I'm coming.

1:11:11.980 --> 1:11:12.980
 It's a counter.

1:11:12.980 --> 1:11:13.980
 Yeah.

1:11:13.980 --> 1:11:14.980
 Yes.

